5:
It's been a while since you've been
here, right? ...Do you need a moment?
14:
I wonder what the Gaean Navy
thinks happened to you.
17:
Well... More than likely, 
they think I died in the line of duty...
21:
Then there's no reason to sneak
around, is there?
25:
Yeah. If anything, we're the ones
likely to attract unwanted
attention—we're pretty well-known
in these parts...
44:
What were you about to do to
Captain Alk? Answer me!
48:
Ow, ow, ow! Corporal Fluffy! 
It's me! Stand down!
58:
So that man is her sergeant... 
For a moment I thought it might be 
her captain.
61:
It sounds like they were in the same
unit... But it doesn't exactly sound like
a joyful reunion.
65: So... What did you two talk about?
69:
Um... He said they're forming a new
unit, and he wants me to be a part
of it.
71:
He doesn't need an answer right
away. I can take my time.
81: Captain Alk... What should I do?
86:
I'm sorry, Fluffy. I can't make this
decision for you.
93:
...You're right. I'll... give it some
thought...
103: Do you not want to go back?
110:
My head's been spinning ever since
talking to the sergeant... I know it's
my choice, but I just don't know
what to do!
116:
My unit's job was to infiltrate and
neutralize enemy ships.
119:
All my teammates were people
brought together by our captain...
124:
He taught me so many things, like
survival skills, fighting techniques,
and the mindset of a soldier...
127:
And he always drilled it into us that
we were all tools.
130:
Despite that... When I was in trouble,
he...
134:
I don't have any more connections
to this world or the Navy... Not
anymore.
137:
...But there's still one thing I want to
know.
139: Why did he... protect a tool like me?
143:
I don't think even he would know the
answer to that question.
151: But you still want to know.
162:
Turns out your captain here has
something to say.
169:
And I certainly don't plan on taking
back what I said about making your
own decision...
173:
But I just want you to know that I'd
miss you if you left. So I personally
would like to see you stay with us.
182:
That's not an order or anything. It's
not even a request. I just wanted to
let you know.
186:
I'm sorry for not saying something
earlier. You never know how another
person feels if they don't tell you,
right?
190:
...That's right. There's a lot of things 
I don't know—and may never find
out...
198:
I... I miss him... I miss the man who
made all those meals for me...
206: I want to stay... with you all!
210:
Okay, in that case, we'll stick
together.
216:
Once again, welcome to Starview
Village, Fluffy.
231: No problem! Leave it to me!
233:
I'll protect you and everyone else...
by my own choice!
